com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Class RemoteSupplierEvaluationResponseService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.RemoteSupplierEvaluationResponseService

  • public class RemoteSupplierEvaluationResponseService
extends Object

    This communication scenario enables a remote system to read supplier evaluation response containing results of supplier evaluations per supplier from the SAP S/4HANA tenant. The remote system calls the synchronous OData service API_SUPLR_EVAL_RESPONSE.

    Business Documentation

    Details:

    OData Service: API_SUPLR_EVAL_RESPONSE_SRV
    API Version: 1
    Minimum ERP Version: 1708
    Communication Scenario: Supplier Evaluation Response Integration (SAP_COM_0139)
    Scope Items: Supplier Evaluation and Performance Monitoring (SL4)
